Remember my comments on the rules of warfare. They only hold so long as all
sides think war is meant to be fair.

Gosh. . .didn\'t mean to be this long-winded. . .

J Roberson      Priss@io.com            Est. 1973
The truth is that the world ended long ago - what we\'re living is the
