the TL13+ ship is cheaper.  The hull is cheaper.  The power plant is
REALLY cheaper.  The guns aren\'t really any cheaper ( a small amount, if
you\'re using the local currency exchanges in TCS), but they ARE more
effective.  Ditto the computers.  Ditto pretty much everything else that
really runs up the price of a warship...but overall, the TL13 ship is
significantly cheaper...

