credit, a TL13 culture will be able to afford 25% - 50% more ships than
a TL12 culture.   And each ship will be better.  Of course, the TL13
culture won\'t usually bother to match the TL12 culture in numbers.
Instead, they will concentrate on their qualitative superiority, which
STILL means that the TL13 ships will be cheaper than similar sized
ships from the TL12 culture.  And the TL13 ships will be considerably
more effective than the similiarly-sized TL12 ships...



