>weapons (10 barrels, chambered in .577/.450, nasty critter) made by Maxim?

The Maxim Gun is not really one weapon.  Maxims started out as a less-bulky
version of the Gatling (in some cases water-cooled).  Later models of Maxim 
were much more like the standard machinegun of today; single barrel, fed by 
belt or large magazine.  Unlike the Gatling, Maxims were generally much 
more portable, but lacked the man-killing (or ship-killing) effectiveness of a 
