Hi!

Could anyone tell me the powers that a typical high-tech (TL B+) police
officer had in the Imperium?  I\'m thinking not so much about police
powers (which of course varies) but about the tools available to him: ie.
what new tools does new technology give the police officer?  And how
would PC\'s -- which are currently suffering a \'small legal
misunderstanding\' in the local system -- find a way to foil this?  Can
they? (I have heard of a TL F robot that can *perfectly* tell if a lie is
being used)

A micro-review of police duties: finding and apprehending criminals
                                 a reliance of non-lethal use of force
                                 crowd control
                                 detective equipment
                                 patrolling the streets/cyberspace/near space
                                      /ocean/roads/air-raft lanes
                                 aid and assisstance

Also: which worlds (and governments) would be most likely to equip their
   police forces with starships?  How would police from Imperial worlds
behave
   outside of their juristicion?  What about extradition treaties?

How would the less ethical police forces operate?  The best police?
   Religious police?  TL 2 police?  And how would they all interact?
   What about if a TL 6 bobby meets a TL C space pirate, but doesn\'t
   feel the need to die right now - what could he do?  How does officers
   on vacuum worlds differ from officers on waterworlds?  What are the
   differences between a cop on a pop6, TL A world w/ tainted atmosphere
   and a cop who has spent her entire time pursuing TL G credit fraud?

Could a low-tech cop even hope to deal with high-tech fraud?
   Disguises?  Violence?  Pirates?  What about the differences between a
   Vargr cop, an Aslan cop, a Zhodani cop, a Droyne cop, a Hiver cop, a
   K\'ree cop, a Solomani cop, a Vilani cop, and a Imperial cop?  Who\'s
   the better officer, a TL8 Aslan cop on a pop 8 world, or a TL F Imperial
   cop on a pop 5 world?

And, just for fun, how would all these cops deal with a speeder?

Any worlds from local law enforcement authorities are appreciated.




----
Alvin Plummer
