taking that into account when putting together your fleets/forces 
can make you LESS vulnerable, thus moving this into the "benefits"
column.

    From what I have seen in TNE and FF&S, dependency on bases/yards
is not nearly so restrictive as it was in earlier forms of the game.
Maintenance may be done "in the field" if parts are provided, and
highly skilled engineering crew are available (all "blue-water"
Navies should have this as a matter of course)

    Note also that, as a matter of course, the generic TLF yard does
