    'body' => 'One idea posted was to figure out why this *doesn\'t* happen.  Since as I
recall
the original scenario talked about was to be CT with the TNE system, at least
small, jump capable rocks won\'t be able to get to relativistic velocities
(but
in CT, the common scout ship could be a planet killer (I\'ll have to do the
math
one of these nights).

>>>>>	Lets assume that a small ship starts far enough out system to be out
