propulsion system GUARANTEES a hit.  Serendip Belt tried this against
Neubayern just before the end of the game - aim at their world, then
if they shoot you, you hit their world, doing far more damage than
would have been done if you allowed them to bombard your world...
    This only works if you detect the rock BEFORE it is aimed at you.
And you won\'t, since Trav sensors aren\'t good enough for that...


