    Fascinating!  Really!  You conjecture that actually hitting a 
planet is next to impossible with a fast rock because it cannot 
change course quickly enough to hit the planet.  On the other hand,
you CAN hit a much smaller target, moving much faster (the rock)
with EXACTLY THE SAME WEAPON THAT COULDN\'T POSSIBLY HIT THE PLANET...
    Think, man!!!


