My concern (just so you all know :) is to make the universe "work", having
said that, I have the following comment:

Maybe battles are different in character than we had thought.  Since many 
factors were ignored (or not even thought of) by GDW, things like "rocks" can
really screw up the game universe. (though they are a reality, so we\'ll have
to learn to live with them :)    Perhaps battles are longer affairs than
represented by High Guard, TCS, or even BR.  These systems show us what happens
