jumps in-system, and looks around.  Their linked (why not?) passive sensors have
decent enough resolution to at least identify large vessels and planets with a 
couple hours observation.  They deploy to attack over a wide area, perhaps 
launching some KE weapons at stationary targets (planets, bases, etc).  Over the
course of hours and even days, the battle dances around----if you\'ve tried BR 
