        More accurately the 1 pS boundary for our Sun is 492.148  solar
        diameters = 4.5775 AU.  To traval from the Earth at 1 AU to the
        Sun\'s 1 pS boundary takes the following travel times:

        M-Drive   Travel Time
        ----   ----
        1G        5 days 08 hr 31 min
        2G        3 days 18 hr 53 min
        3G        3 days 02 hr 12 min
        4G        2 days 16 hr 16 min
        5G        2 days 09 hr 29 min
        6G        2 days 04 hr 28 min



