    'body' => '4) Customs:  This is an area largely ignored in the rules that I\'ve
tried to stay on top of in my own games.  Just the environmental
regulations governing shipments of goods from one ecosystem to
another must be so vast and complex that they can only be handled
by computer.  Because the Imperium allows member worlds to
exercise considerable autonomy -- even to the point of going to
war with each other -- it probably does not try to govern
interstellar commerce like Congress tries to govern interstate
commerce (it doesn\'t in my universe, anyway).  Consequently,
import and export regulations (besides the environmental ones) are
