devestated, and the Terrans needed time to rebuild. When 
Virus came, the Terrans were still in the early stages of 
rebuilding their area of space. Since they were rebuilding 
virtually everything - and that includes replacing 
destroyed or worn out electronic equipment and starships, 
Terran scientists were able to recognize Virus as a problem 
and deal with it. As always, I will solicit any comments. <<

I like this. It provides a relief from the general air of 
destruction. And - let\'s be honest - most of us would have 
liked Good O\' Earth to pull through. After all, we were all 
dead pleased to find it\'d made it to the 57th Century, 
weren\'t we ?




