it\'s interesting how the same topics keep raising their heads (asteroid
throwing, defence of gas giants, keeping FGMPs and battledress out of player
hands, etc.).

Oh, and "Salisbury, Tim" <salisbury@ftdetrck-atmo1.army.mil> had a title
