protection that every government makes in exchange for the tribute you
pay them), and if they\'re "the bad guys" (undiluted pond scum), then
they act like most governments, and only protect their citizens when
it is convenient to do so.  And where\'s Luke Skywalker when you need
him, anyway? ;-)

                ----Steve


