a brief summary, of course, but the whole thing smacked of a 
bad teen horror movie - everybody is scared of the big boogyman 
until they realize it is all just a dream and wake up.  Gaaaa!!!

So - I suspect GDW will still make use of the hanging threads left 
over from this (some TNS excerpts and similar hints).  Anybody got 
any ideas as to what we will see?  Or will this sort of disappear like 
the hints of a K\'Kree invasion did right before TNE came out?  My 
own guess is a rebellion by one of the non-human subject races in the 
Consulate.  Given the psionic nature of the Consulate, it would be pretty 
tough to have a prole rebellion.  Or, there could be some sort of a group 
of psionic overlords who have decided to spread their psionic rule 
regardless of the desires of the Consulate.  To do this, they must first 
sieze control of the Consulate.  When the Regency Sourcebook comes 
out, some of the more bloody-minded gamers may find it a dull place.  
