Oh and I don\'t disagree with that analysis either.   I do take New Bedford,
MA as a for instance.  During the whaling days this was a real happening
place. Now there isn\'t much happening there...  Other towns can be used as
examples here.

>Oh, and Peter\'s comments about container shipping is a good one, but
