At 43G it goes 0 to 60 in .12 seconds. Unfortunately its
sensors only give you about 5 seconds to swerve to avoid
that upcoming mountain range.
 There are Diesel Locomotives, Merchant ships, Mobile
Homes, Battle Cruisers, Urban Vehicles, and Interceptors.
