other kind or length.   Please, post in context to this 
list... or take it to the TML.   <<

_Mister_ Kundert, if you\'d _bothered_ to actually read the 
design properly, you would possibly have spotted that it is 
_not_ a TNE design. I don\'t use TNE. The design is (with 
house variants) Megatraveller. A high-handed and 
ill-informed assault of this nature is a splendid way to 
attract more epithets, though such is not my way. 

>>  Also, almost every CT ship was converted to MT WAAAY 
back  when MT first came out.  Seeing them done again does 
nothing  for my database of Trav ships (rather over a 
hundred designs just  from my last TCS game, much less the 
hundreds more (thousands?)  from the TML over the years)... <<

There are already people on the list who don\'t have and 
can\'t get these, as MT is now defunct.  There are also 
probably a fair number of people who are as new to the list 
(ie 1 year or so) as I am, and haven\'t had the benefit of 
these designs. I\'ve seen about 20-25 all the time I\'ve been 
here. 

The major source of such conversions is FSSI. IMHO, the 
designs in there are terrible. If you look closely, some of 
the old CT designs can be seen, reduced from named classes 
with some personality to a stack of numbers. Plus, the 
designs don\'t work - and the armour values! Some (repeat: 
some!) of my designs are (seriously improved and annotated) 
versions of these, which I\'ve found quite useful in my own game. 

OK, so it does nothing for you; a lot of the stuff I\'ve 
seen on here did nothing for me (eg stuff on the TCS 
subsectors, etc), but I passed over it and went on, 
confident that there were folk happy to see it. I rather 
hoped there might be a) a few people out there who might 
like a few ships and b) a bit of tolerance from those who 
didn\'t need them. There was only 25 lines or so for 
Christ\'s sake! 

I started with a chestnut so\'s people could get the hang of 
my design style, fully intending to trot out some unusual 
stuff further on. To be honest I don\'t know if I can be 
bothered after this. Come on you lot, we\'re all gamers 
playing the same game for fun. We\'ve got enough enemies 
without pissing each other off.

Sorry in advance if this has irritated anybody. Such is 
genuinely not my intention. 


