>Perhaps a splinter group of Vargr would make a religion out of worshipping
>their "ancestors" ?

I think, more than anything else, this thread has been more of a reflection
of what human attutides in the Imperium would be toward the Vargr.   It is
also an example of what I think Vargr would really find offensive, the
human attitudes toward how they think they should relate to animals.  The
implication here is that Vargr are just "trumped up dogs" and should see
them as brothers.  After all, do you see anyone proposing that humans in
the Imperium should worship monkeys?  Do we regard monkeys as "ancestors"?
No we regard _people_ as ancestors.
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^


Well I believe I\'ve heard of some religion that had "monkey gods". Can\'t
say for sure though but I don\'t think it\'s beyond reason.

Phil


