employing it when inappropriate and vice versa.
(5) No understanding of poetic speech (e.g. "Your hair is like a 
laughing brook, rippling in the breeze" becomes "Wanna f**k")
(6) Uses baby talk ("what an ickle sweet little Zhodani you are! Daddy 
get you a loll-loll!")
(7) Deliberately mistranslates

