But the idea is great in itself! Maybe rats couldn\'t survive
this treatment very well, but it\'s a good guess that vermin
exists in the Traveller universe that could survive this and
maybe even rougher treatment.

So starships could be infested with extraterrestrial bugs of the
referee\'s own device. Slimy things, poisonous things,
disease-carriers, destructive little vermin, even cute animals
if the referee is in a playful mood.

