Ooh, you\'re touching upon a sensitive subject here...

>If I lived in Ilelish I would prefer Lucan to an idealistic incompetent
>like Dulinor.

We\'ll I wouldn\'t. Dulinor may be an idealistic incompetent (some of
his actions points in that direction) but at least he\'s not an "evil" type
dictator. Most war crimes during the Rebellion seems to be
committed by Lucan\'s forces.

>(not to mention that if I were Lucan I would have had psionic body
