    'day' => '17',
    'body' => 'oh..I see that nobody agrees with me..
All the arguments that have been made make sense of course,
and it is very hard to touch upon these issues without
becoming..politically incorrect..I will try to approach
the border line with the following statement::On earth today
the countries with the highest production TL (and this is what the
TL is) are less violent than the ones with lower TL.

Two possible reasons:
1- higher TL = better lifestyle, more money = less will to kill
and torture somebody else for silly reasons

2- higher TL = higher development = higher general cultural 
development(and this is a fact of history, on  average)

So I would reiterate (for the last time, I promise) that everthing
is at has been described in the traveller universe, but I would
expect that in the 56th century real world either we have killed each other
completely or the world will be less violent than it is now (as
far as humans are concerned).
            Max

----
